<paragraph id="742491AED40EE3C1B2919D21611077C5" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F34F5CC4FEBB075160D1605E631CB2EF" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">
TENERIFE: Santa 
<normalizedToken id="EE2DF5FE5A0866ACB7F1DEC795C25FC2" originalValue="Úrsula">Ursula</normalizedToken>
, La Quinta, alongside dirt tracks, rather numerous in two localities, 11.12.2018, 
